com.stackmob.sdk.api
Class StackMobQueryWithField

java.lang.Object
  com.stackmob.sdk.api.StackMobQueryWithField

public class StackMobQueryWithField
extends Object

Represents a query being executed on a specific field. This is meant to be used as part of a chain with StackMobQuery, and will be generated when you use StackMobQuery. add the constraints you want and the call getQuery() to get a query suitable for passing into a query function.
StackMobQuery query = new StackMobQuery("user").field("age").isGreaterThan(20).isLessThanOrEqualTo(40).field("friend").in(Arrays.asList("joe", "bob", "alice").getQuery();
